 target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png" width="561" height="523" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/aa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:523,&quot;width&quot;:561,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:208442,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://pubs.rsc.org/en/content/articlehtml/2021/ee/d0ee02681f">Ziegler &amp; Trancik (2021)</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这种改进的大部分<a href="https://news.mit.edu/2021/lithium-ion-battery-cost-1122">归功于研发工作</a>，但工业规模效应也开始产生重大影响。</p><p>当然，这仍然留下了电池的<em>用途</em>这一基本问题。我将介绍一系列用例，从明显的（汽车和能源存储）到不那么明显的。但首先，我应该谈谈<em>为什么</em>电池是一种通用技术。</p><h4>电池同时解决了两个基本问题</h4><p>能源显然是工业社会各个领域的基础，对于运输、制造、电力和电器等物理（“原子”）技术尤其重要。我们经常从<em>初级</em>能源的角度来思考——也就是说，我们从哪里获得能量。太阳能、风能、核能和水力发电等技术满足了这一需求，当然燃烧化石燃料也能满足这一需求。电池不会这样做。</p><p>但能源不仅仅是发电。我们还必须<em>储存</em>能量，并且必须将其从一个地方<em>运输</em>到另一个地方。换句话说，我们必须在时间和空间上移动能量，以便我们可以随时随地使用它。电池可以解决这两个问题。</p><p>在存储方面，电池还不如化石燃料，因为它们会随着时间的推移而泄漏能量。这就是为什么它们可以用于发电厂和电网的短期储能，但不能用于季节性储能。但在能源运输方面，电池在某些方面优于化石燃料。首先，电池基本上可以通过任何电源充电，而石油管道或天然气罐只能容纳一种特定类型的化石燃料。其次，从电池中提取能量通常比使用内燃机提取能量的噪音小得多。还有其他优点。</p><p>但最重要的是，电池不需要庞大的内燃机来提取能量。当我在 2020 年夏天读到波特兰抗议者<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yEqRIkVEya0">使用电池驱动的吹叶机向联邦特工吹回催泪瓦斯</a>时，我第一次意识到了这一点的重要性。电池驱动的吹叶机的功率不如汽油驱动的吹叶机，但<a href="https://www.gardentoolexpert.com/electric-vs-gas-leaf-blowers-what-do-you-choose/">它们也轻得多</a>。这就是我们为小型轻型无人机使用电池的原因。这是您的智能手机配备电池而不是小型汽油发动机的一个重要原因。</p><p>每当电池怀疑论者告诉您电池的能量密度比化石燃料“更低”时，请向他们指出这一点。</p><p>随着电池的不断改进，它们与化石燃料相比的缺点将会减少。我们将开发寿命更长、功率密度更大等的电池。</p><h4>明显的用例——汽车和电力存储</h4><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F70980ee9-2611-40e4-a56d-530570a8bbe9_1024x766.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F70980ee9-2611-40e4-a56d-530570a8bbe9_1024x766.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F70980ee9-2611-40e4-a56d-530570a8bbe9_1024x766.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/ht